{"tid":2446502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 港超賽事再有球迷 47 分鐘以口號掌聲　聲援民主派 47 人 】","createTime":"2021-03-14T13:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T16:33:59.000Z","uid":126919,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2210cd31a66a26d7b9d8dc129f96b6771f99f405","tid":2446502,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"【 港超賽事再有球迷 47 分鐘以口號掌聲　聲援民主派 47 人 】<br />\n <br />\n今晚香港超級足球聯賽賽事，標準流浪對傑志於青衣運動場舉行，繼上個比賽週後，再有球迷在比賽第 47 分鐘鼓掌，聲援因參與或組織民主派初選、後被控「串謀顛覆國家政權」的 47 人，亦有人多次高叫「撐手足」等口號。<br />\n <br />\n本月初的兩場港超賽事，在旺角大球場舉行的冠忠南區對東方龍獅，以及東方龍獅對傑志，分別都有球迷在第 47 分鐘鼓掌，及高叫「撐手足」。至今已經最少有三個港超比賽日，有球迷在第 47 分鐘鼓掌、叫口號聲援。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1052294701926958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1052294701926958&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=60c64eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1052294701926958</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726f762252d98379568532103cfd27bb00415a63","tid":2446502,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1cea63e646c0aa97def038878c62c719c0f958","tid":2446502,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a